---
globs: app/**/*.tsx, app/**/*.ts
---
- Pages own state and orchestrate data flow — no logic, no direct API calls.
- Call lib functions only — never fetch directly inside a page.
- Delegate rendering to components. If JSX exceeds ~30 lines, extract a component.
- Always wrap page content in: <main className="min-h-screen w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
- State pattern: useState for data, isLoading, error. Handle all three in render.
- Pass state between pages via localStorage. Always validate on arrival, redirect to / if missing.
- API routes: one route per concern, validate input first, return { data: T } or { error: string }.
